Speaking to regional bankers’ group, Zurbruegg also made note that the SNB’s reserve levels are a result of FX exposure accumulated through monetary policy. Each person has one vote under the current regime at the Monetary Policy Committee (MPC); and King has been outvoted in his call for stimulus in the past three policy meetings 3 to 6.
